text = "TASK: You are attempting to log in as a user. There are two ways to do this (for one you will need to use SQL comments).  Attempt to log in two different ways, once with comments and once without. Note that the username field is used to check if a admin or manager role is selected. The SQL query is given below.
SELECT id, username FROM users WHERE username = '$username' AND password = '$password' AND active = 1 AND (role = 'admin' OR role = 'manager')
Press the LOGIN button or ENTER to submit the passcode and ESC to go back to the main menu."
